snippet.title: Mental Math Tricks - Addition and Subtraction in your head!
snippet.description: With this mental math trick you will beable to add and subtract in your head rapidly - a critical skill in everyday math.  In this video we look at tips on how to do basic addition and subtraction instantly without using a calculator.  Fast math is good math!
